INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('1193', '1', '2014-03-18 05:55:01', '2014-03-18 05:55:01', '<img class=\"alignright  wp-image-1138\" alt=\"attorney_pic\" src=\"http://carlspector.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/attorney_pic.png\" width=\"172\" height=\"207\" />My name is Carl Spector  and I am committed to criminal defense and the defense of DWI / DUI cases.\r\n\r\nI am a graduate of the State University of New York at Buffalo where I received a bachelors degree in Communication. I received my legal education at New York Law School and Nova Southeastern University where I received my Juris Doctorate.\r\n\r\nI am licensed to practice in New York, New Jersey and Florida (inactive) and the United States District Court Southern and Eastern Districts of New York and the District Court of New Jersey.\r\n\r\nI assist clients all over New York City including Manhattan, Brooklyn, Queens, Staten Island and the Bronx, and in Nassau County, Suffolk County, Westchester County and Rockland County.\r\n\r\n<strong>Experience</strong>\r\n\r\nI worked as an attorney in the Bronx County District Attorneys office as an Assistant District Attorney for six years.\r\n<a href=\"http://www.avvo.com/attorneys/10005-ny-carl-spector-876845.html?utm_campaign=avvo_rating&amp;utm_content=1217583&amp;utm_medium=avvo_badge&amp;utm_source=avvo\"><img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-1194\" alt=\"Avvo_Badge\" src=\"http://carlspector.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Avvo_Badge.png\" width=\"133\" height=\"108\" /></a>\r\nI truly believe my experience as a former prosecutor makes me uniquely suited to effectively and aggressively defend my clients charged with all varieties of crimes and DWI / DUI.\r\n\r\nFor the past twenty-two (22) years I have been representing people that have been charged with crimes throughout New York City, Rockland, Westchester and Nassau Counties and the state of New Jersey. I have served as an attorney in countless criminal and DWI / DUI matters with full control of initial investigations, trial planning, motions, discovery, legal research and courtroom appearances and trials.\r\n\r\nI have analyzed forensic evidence regarding arson investigations, developing a theory of litigation based on that analysis and have cross examined many police officers, detectives, expert witnesses including arson and explosives experts, electronic experts, ballistics experts, police laboratory chemists, physicians and psychologists.\r\n\r\nI have successfully litigated and argued many pre-trial motions to suppress evidence based on probable cause to stop and frisk and violations of the defendants Fifth and Fourteenth Amendment rights. In 2009 I served as the Municipal Prosecutor in the large Bergen County municipality of Fair Lawn. I was reappointed to that position for 2010 and 2011. I was appointed by the Mayor and Counsel of Municipality Fair Lawn to serve as the alternate Public Defender in 2012, 2013 and 2014.\r\n\r\nMy New York defense practice areas and experience include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>DWI / DUI</li>\r\n	<li>Driving Under the Influence of Drugs</li>\r\n	<li>Marijuana Refusal Hearings</li>\r\n	<li>Driving While Suspended</li>\r\n	<li>Marijuana Possession Marijuana Sale</li>\r\n	<li>Identity Theft</li>\r\n	<li>Credit Card Fraud</li>\r\n	<li>Insurance Fraud</li>\r\n	<li>Drug Possession</li>\r\n	<li>Drug Sale</li>\r\n	<li>Conspiracy Charges</li>\r\n	<li>Assault</li>\r\n	<li>Domestic Violence</li>\r\n	<li>Gun Possession</li>\r\n	<li>Gun Use</li>\r\n	<li>Robbery</li>\r\n	<li>Burglary</li>\r\n	<li>Sex Crimes</li>\r\n	<li>Murder</li>\r\n	<li>Attempted Murder</li>\r\n	<li>Grand Larceny</li>\r\n	<li>Receiving Stolen Property</li>\r\n	<li>Petit Larceny</li>\r\n	<li>Menacing</li>\r\n	<li>Criminal Mischief</li>\r\n	<li>Trespass</li>\r\n	<li>Shoplifting</li>\r\n	<li>Speeding Cases</li>\r\n	<li>Red Light Violations</li>\r\n	<li>Criminal Record Expungements</li>\r\n	<li>Leaving the Scene of an Accident</li>\r\n	<li>Probation Violations</li>\r\n	<li>Parole Violations</li>\r\n	<li>Felonies</li>\r\n	<li>Misdemeanors</li>\r\n	<li>Wrongful Arrest</li>\r\n	<li>Excessive Use of Force</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nI am a member of the following professional organizations: New York State Criminal Bar Association, New York State Bar Association, American Bar Association, New Jersey State Municipal Prosecutors Association, Bergen County Bar Association.', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1139-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-03-18 05:55:01', '2014-03-18 05:55:01', '', '1139', 'http://carlspector.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/1139-autosave-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
