INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('1235', '1', '2011-09-17 07:02:42', '2011-09-17 07:02:42', 'In certain counties across New York State prosecutors have established veterans treatment court programs to divert veterans who have been arrested for non-violent offenses including DWI charges for treatment in lieu of the traditional trial and punishment.\r\n\r\nThe program requires the veterans to get mental health or addiction counseling, find jobs, stay clean and sober and get their lives back on track.\r\n\r\nThe criminal case is reviewed every month to monitor the progress to make certain that all appointments and obligations are being met by the veteran and that the judge is kept updated on the progress of each case.\r\n\r\nThe cases tend to remain in treatment court a year or more before making enough progress to graduate and see their charges reduced or dismissed.', 'New York Veterans Treatment Court  For DWI Cases', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'new-york-veterans-treatment-court-for-dwi-cases', '', '', '2014-03-18 07:05:13', '2014-03-18 07:05:13', '', '0', 'http://carlspector.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/?p=1235', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('1236', '1', '2014-03-18 07:05:42', '2014-03-18 07:05:42', '<h3>Call Us Today To Learn How We Can Help You</h3>\r\nA DWI arrest is a scary experience. One minute, its a day like any other. The next, theres a giant question mark hanging over your whole life. Maybe you failed the field sobriety test, or maybe your breath test result was over the legal limit. If youve been arrested for DWI, DWAI, or DUI on Long Island, we can help.\r\n\r\nOur attorneys have more than eight decades of DWI experience in New York, but more importantly, as former prosecutors, we know the prosecutions playbook. We know how the case will proceed in the courts, and we can spot the strengths  and the weaknesses  in the prosecutions case. After all, we have a combined four decades of experience prosecuting DUI cases in New York, and we are committed to aggressively defending your rights.\r\n\r\nWere The Right Attorneys For Your DUI Defense\r\n\r\nAs former New York prosecutors with strong ties to law enforcement, we have the insight and experience to shift the balance in New York DWI/DWAI/DUI cases  increasing the odds of the kind of outcome that lets you get on with your life. Our team is extremely effective in handling DUI defense, and well do everything we can to secure the best possible outcome for your case.\r\n\r\nAfter a DWI arrest, a lot of people feel like theres nothing to be done in their case, but our experience gives us the perspective to spot the problems in the prosecutions case. From police procedural issues to badly calibrated testing equipment and more, our team is the right team to exploit problems in your case.\r\n\r\nWhat Happens To Me Now?\r\n\r\nThe aftermath of a DUI arrest is a confusing and frightening time. Youre flooded with emotions and concerned about your reputation and your future. What happens to you from here? Will a DWI charge affect your job? Your license? Will you have to go to jail? Will this incident follow you around for the rest of your life?\r\n\r\nWe know you have a lot of questions. By calling today, we can help you answer them. We dont do high pressure and we wont give you the run around.\r\n\r\nWell listen to your story, ask you some questions, and tell you if we think we can help.\r\nThe call is free, and you have no obligations.\r\n\r\nOur only concern is providing you with practical, effective advice. We are a team committed to aggressive defense of your DWI/DWAI/DUI case, and we will do everything we can to secure the best outcome possible.', 'Long Island NY DUI-DWI Defense', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'long-island-ny-dui-dwi-defense', '', '', '2014-03-18 07:05:42', '2014-03-18 07:05:42', '', '0', 'http://carlspector.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/?page_id=1236', '0', 'page', '', '0');
INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('1237', '1', '2014-03-18 07:06:31', '2014-03-18 07:06:31', '<h3>Our team of former New York prosecutors can be the difference between a big hassle and a big win in your DWI defense.</h3>\r\nTheres really only one reason that people find our website, and thats because you or someone you love has gone through the ordeal of being arrested for DWI, DWAI, or DUI in Rockland County, New York. Its a traumatic experience, and youre left with so many questions: Will you lose your license? Will you have to go to jail? What if your employer finds out? What does a DUI arrest mean for your family?\r\n\r\nTheres so much to think about, but your first step is finding the right team to support you and fight for you.\r\n\r\nWe think were that team\r\n\r\nWe are former New York prosecutors, so we know how a DWI case is built and conducted, and we know the problems most DWI prosecutors try to gloss over. We look for:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The weak spots in the prosecutions case, and exploit them</li>\r\n	<li>Flaws in law enforcement procedure, and use them</li>\r\n	<li>Problems with sobriety testing methodology or equipment, and hammer them home</li>\r\n	<li>And more  there are literally dozens of potential flaws in any DWI prosecution, and we know where to look and how to spot them.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe have been winning Criminal and DWI cases in New York for nearly eight decades, using our combined forty years of experience as New York prosecutors as the foundation of our commitment to a forceful and aggressive DWI defense in Rockland County. We are reliable, knowledgeable, and experienced  exactly the kind of steady team you want standing beside you in tough spots.\r\n\r\nLets start getting your life back. Give us a call.\r\n\r\nYour situation feels challenging, but a DWI arrest doesnt have to beat you. The first step in taking control of your life again is to call  not for a sales pitch or to be pressured into something, but to talk to a courteous, knowledgeable Rockland County DWI expert. Our friendly staff will listen to your story. Well ask you a few questions to make sure we understand what happened to you. Then well tell you  honestly  if we think we can help.\r\n\r\nWeve been providing DWI defense in Rockland County for many, many years now, and there arent a lot of instances where we cant offer sound advice and a sound defense. We are absolutely committed to achieving the best outcome possible in your DWI case, and we will do everything we can to secure it for you.', 'Rockland NY DUI-DWI Defense', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'rockland-ny-dui-dwi-defense', '', '', '2014-03-18 07:06:31', '2014-03-18 07:06:31', '', '0', 'http://carlspector.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/?page_id=1237', '0', 'page', '', '0');
