INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('1244', '1', '2014-03-18 07:08:20', '2014-03-18 07:08:20', '<h3>We are former New York prosecutors, and we know how to take on the prosecutions DWI case against you.</h3>\r\nAfter a DWI or DUI arrest, most people are pretty scared. You probably have a million questions about whats going to happen, and deep concerns about your future. Will you still be able to drive? Are you going to lose your job? Will you have to go to jail? Will this follow you around for the rest of your life?\r\n\r\nWe understand. Our team of reliable, experienced attorneys has been defending DWI and DUI cases in Rochester for years, and we know what youre going through. We are absolutely committed to an aggressive, forthright defense of your rights, and we will do everything we can to achieve the best possible outcome in your case.\r\n\r\nBut I failed the sobriety test. What can you do?\r\n\r\nA lot of people come away from the experience of a DWI arrest feeling like theres nothing to be done in their defense. We can assure you that its probably not true. As ex-prosecutors in New York, we know how DWI prosecutions happen and we know what may have gone wrong on the law enforcement side. We know how prosecutors gloss over problems in a case, and we can spot  and exploit  the weaknesses in their case against you.\r\n\r\nMaybe you failed a field sobriety test or had a breath test over the legal limit, but that doesnt mean your case is closed. In Rochester, testing equipment has to be properly calibrated, administering personnel have to be properly trained, and you can only be stopped by police if they have genuine probable cause. There are literally dozens of reasons why your arrest may have been improper or your test results incorrect, and we want to help you prove it.\r\n\r\nFor Tough, Effective DUI Defense, Call Today\r\n\r\nWe know prosecutors and law enforcement, and thats what makes us so effective at DUI defense.\r\n\r\nWhen you call, you will talk to a courteous member of our team who wants to hear your story. Well probably ask you a few questions to make sure we understand what happened to you. Then well tell you what we think we can do about it.\r\n\r\nIts simple, its easy, and its totally free. We wont give you the run around and we wont lay any pressure on you. You can even email us using the form on the right side of the screen if you cant call right now. Well get back to you when its convenient for you.\r\n\r\nWe want to give you the best possible advice. Call us at 585-563-4601 today for your free, no-pressure consultation, and take the first step in getting your life back.', 'Rochester NY DUI-DWI Defense', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'rochester-ny-dui-dwi-defense', '', '', '2014-03-18 07:08:20', '2014-03-18 07:08:20', '', '0', 'http://carlspector.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/?page_id=1244', '0', 'page', '', '0');
INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('1245', '1', '2014-03-18 07:08:51', '2014-03-18 07:08:51', '<h3>Dont take chances with your DUI defense in Albany. Our experienced ex-prosecutors can make the difference in your case.</h3>\r\nYouve probably found this page because you or someone you love was recently arrested for DWI, DWAI, or DUI in the Albany, New York, area. Its a scary time and youre probably wondering what comes next for you and your family.\r\n\r\nWe can help. We are an experienced team of Criminal and DUI Defense attorneys with more than eight decades of combined experience practicing in Albany, New York. But even better, we are also former New York prosecutors who know exactly what steps the prosecution will take in your DWI case.\r\n\r\nRight now youre probably wondering whether youll lose your license, how your employer will react, and even if youll have to go to jail. We can help you  we are committed to an aggressive defense of your rights and privileges in your DWI fight, and we will do everything we can to ensure the most favorable outcome possible for you.\r\n\r\nWe fight for you on all sides\r\n\r\nPeople often feel like theres nothing they can do to fight a DWI charge after an arrest, but dont lose hope. In our experience, there are questions to be raised about every step of a DWI/DUI case, from determining whether the initial stop was legal, to finding out exactly who administered, handled, and processed any testing that may have been performed, and more. As ex-prosecutors, we have built cases against DWI defendants, and we know exactly where to look to find the weaknesses in the prosecutions case and how best to exploit every one.\r\n\r\nIf youve been arrested for DWI in Albany, we want to help you. Our courteous, interested team is available 24 hours a day, seven days a week, and we want to hear your story. When you call, well listen to you, ask you a few questions to make sure we understand exactly what happened to you, and give you our honest opinion of whether or not we can help you.\r\n\r\nWith our long experience in DWI cases, there arent many instances in which we cant help. The call is entirely free, and well never pressure you in any way. Well give you the best advice we can, and if you choose us to defend you, well give you the best defense we can.\r\n\r\nStart to close the book on your DWI. Call us at 518-478-2418 today for your free, no obligation consultation. If you prefer email, just use the contact form on the right side of your screen and well get back to you when its convenient for you.\r\n\r\nA DWI doesnt have to derail your life. Well help you get back on track by fighting for the best outcome available in your situation.', 'Albany NY DUI-DWI Defense', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'albany-ny-dui-dwi-defense', '', '', '2014-03-18 07:08:51', '2014-03-18 07:08:51', '', '0', 'http://carlspector.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/?page_id=1245', '0', 'page', '', '0');
INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('1246', '1', '2014-03-18 07:10:30', '2014-03-18 07:10:30', '<h3>We have prosecuted DWI cases and our team of DWI defenders knows how to fight back for you.</h3>\r\nHave you gone through the awful experience of a DWI arrest in Syracuse? If so, you know how scary and disorienting the process is, and were sure you have a lot of questions about what comes next.\r\n\r\nIf youre like most people, after a DWI arrest in Syracuse, youre wondering about your future. You want to know whether you have to lose your drivers license and for how long? Do you have to tell your boss? Will you have to go to jail?\r\n\r\nWe can help you answer those questions\r\n\r\nBut more importantly, we can help you find the best possible answers, because we are committed to aggressively defending DWI cases in Syracuse. We are former prosecutors from around New York, and we know the ins and outs of DWI/DUI cases. We can spot the weak places in the prosecutions arguments, and we can exploit them.\r\n\r\nOften, a person comes away from the DWI arrest experience believing that theres nothing to be done in his or her defense. We can assure you that in our experience, thats usually not the case. Even if you failed a field sobriety test or your breath test showed an elevated reading, its not the end of your options.\r\n\r\nWe approach your case from every angle\r\n\r\nWas your traffic stop legal? Who administered any testing you may have undergone? When was the last time the equipment was calibrated? Who handled any testing samples, and how?\r\n\r\nAnd these are just some of the problems that we routinely see with DWI cases in Syracuse. Our decades of experience in Criminal and DWI defense give us the perspective to find every loose thread in your case and pull  until we unravel it as fully as we can.\r\n\r\nDont believe for a second that theres nothing to be done in your case. Its been our experience that theres nearly always a lot to be done about a DWI arrest, and we want 