INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('1256', '1', '2014-03-18 07:12:30', '2014-03-18 07:12:30', '<h3>Let our team of former New York prosecutors take care of your DWI dilemma.</h3>\r\nA DWI arrest in Niagara Falls is never a good experience, and afterwards youre left with so many questions.\r\n\r\nBeyond concerns about your future, you may also feel that theres nothing you can do. Maybe you failed a field sobriety test and you feel like your case is now closed.\r\n\r\nWe are here to tell you: It isnt.\r\n\r\nWe are former New York prosecutors, so we know exactly how a DWI case is built in Niagara Falls. We know what the most common (and even the less common) problems are with DWI cases, and we know how a prosecutor will try to minimize the defects in a case. Some of those include:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Did the police have probable cause to stop you in the first place?</li>\r\n	<li>What types of sobriety tests were administered?</li>\r\n	<li>Were tests administered by trained, authorized personnel?</li>\r\n	<li>Were samples properly handled?</li>\r\n	<li>Was testing equipment properly calibrated?</li>\r\n	<li>And more</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIn our experience, there are numerous potential problems with every DWI case, and as former prosecutors and experienced DWI defenders in Niagara Falls, we know just what to look for when it comes to defending your case.\r\n\r\nSo dont give up. We wont.\r\n\r\nLets face it, a DWI arrest is a pretty awful experience. One minute, your life is proceeding normally, and the next, you have this giant question mark hanging over your head. The questions we hear over and over again from clients just like you are:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Will I lose my drivers license?</li>\r\n	<li>Do I have to tell my boss?</li>\r\n	<li>Will I have to go to jail?</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThere are so many more, and we want to help you answer them. We can help you make sense of your DWI issue 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, by calling 716-304-0046.\r\n\r\nWhen you call, youll talk to one of our friendly, courteous staff who will listen to your whole story. Probably, well ask some questions to make sure we understand everything correctly. Then, well let you know what we think, and most of all, whether or not we think we can help.\r\n\r\nIn most cases, we can help. We cant turn the clock back and give you a do-over, but we can promise an aggressive, forthright defense of your rights and privileges, in court and in negotiations. We will do everything we can to secure the best possible outcome in your case, taking into account your particular situation.\r\n\r\nWhen you call, we wont put any pressure on you and youll be under no obligation. Think of it as your first step in taking your life back  a free consultation with attorneys who know DWI in Niagara Falls and can help put you in control again.', 'Niagara Falls NY DUI-DWI Defense', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1247-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-18 07:12:30', '2014-03-18 07:12:30', '', '1247', 'http://carlspector.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/1247-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('1257', '1', '2014-03-18 07:13:30', '2014-03-18 07:13:30', '<div>\r\n\r\nOriginally Published On AVVO.com\r\n\r\nIf you needed legal help, would you know where to turn for advice?\r\n\r\nThats where Avvo.com comes in, with profiles, ratings, and reviews of more than 90% of the attorneys across the U.S. By providing the information you need, Avvo empowers consumers like you to choose the right lawyer.\r\n\r\nThis spring, <em>Arrive Magazine </em>and Avvo have teamed up to bring you 50 of the best and brightest attorneys in New York. These 50 lawyers represent Avvos top picks in the following practice areas: DUI, immigration, divorce, personal injury, and criminal defense. The attorneys were carefully selected based on their Avvo Rating, a score from 1 to 10 that is calculated using information from their profiles, including education, work history, prestigious awards, and peer endorsements.\r\n\r\nSo if you are looking for a highly rated attorney near you, this list is a great place to start. If you would like to view more top lawyers in these practice areas or any other, just visit <strong>www.avvo.com</strong>. Not only will you find a great lawyer, youll also be able to ask legal questions in our Q&amp;A forum and research your legal issueall for free.\r\n\r\n<strong>AVVOS LIST OF TOP NEW YORK DWI/DUI LAWYERS</strong>\r\n\r\nSteven Raiser Raiser &amp; Kenniff, PC Mineola, NY <a href=\"tel:888-504-2746\" target=\"_blank\">888-504-2746</a>\r\n\r\nEdward Fiandach Fiandach &amp; Fiandach Rochester, NY <a href=\"tel:800-592-6006\" target=\"_blank\">800-592-6006</a>\r\n\r\nMichael Mohun Law Office of Michael Mohun Cowlesville, NY <a href=\"tel:585-937-8987\" target=\"_blank\">585-937-8987</a>\r\n\r\nThomas Anelli Anelli Xavier, P.C. Syracuse, NY <a href=\"tel:866-792-7800\" target=\"_blank\">866-792-7800</a>\r\n\r\nPeter Gerstenzang Gerstenzang OHern Hickey &amp; Gerstenzang Albany, NY <a href=\"tel:518-456-6456\" target=\"_blank\">518-456-6456</a>\r\n\r\nPeter Brill Brill Legal Group, P.C. Hauppauge, NY <a href=\"tel:888-309-8876\" target=\"_blank\">888-309-8876</a>\r\n\r\nRaymond Sciarrino Sciarrino &amp; Sciarrino, P.C. Perry, NY <a href=\"tel:585-237-4120\" target=\"_blank\">585-237-4120</a>\r\n\r\nBrian Berkowitz Law Office of Brian Berkowitz New City, NY <a href=\"tel:845-638-9200\" target=\"_blank\">845-638-9200</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Carl Spector Law Offices of Carl Spector New York, NY <a href=\"tel:212-683-5912\" target=\"_blank\">212-683-5912</a> <a href=\"www.nyc-criminal-attorneys.com\">www.nyc-criminal-attorneys.com</a></strong>\r\n\r\nEric Zitofsky Eric W Zitofsky Attorney at Law West Haverstraw, NY <a href=\"tel:845-786-7740\" target=\"_blank\">845-786-7740</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSee complete list at: <a href=\"http://www.arrive-digital.com/arrive/20110304?pg=92#pg92\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://www.arrive-digital.com/arrive/20110304?pg=92#pg92</a>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Carl Spector is named to List of Top New York DWI-DUI Lawyers', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1242-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-03-18 07:13:30', '2014-03-18 07:13:30', '', '1242', 'http://carlspector.laptoppricesinpakistan.com.pk/1242-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
